I apologize for the mistake! Thank you for correcting me.

You're welcome for the info on Asana's integration with Google Calendar! I'm glad I could help. It's great that you're looking forward to following up with the gentleman from the prominent software firm. Fingers crossed that it leads to a fruitful collaboration!

If you have any more questions or need further assistance, feel free to ask. Otherwise, I'll let you get back to your event planning and follow-up meeting. Good luck!
